rlos Vellido","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"MX","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Juan Carlos Vellido","primary":true}}]}},"tv_39914_credits":{"at":1773676835680,"data":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":1267410,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Marie Facundo","original_name":"Marie Facundo","popularity":0.5893,"profile_path":"/eLE0ZhNPySr97Qm84THo9DSO4Qw.jpg","character":"Oscar / Popy","credit_id":"6807c69d142b09cecf899d45","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1708251,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Sly Johnson","original_name":"Sly Johnson","popularity":0.3747,"profile_path":"/t1SRSDDpbw6yFjn7tcaPje2FzEA.jpg","character":"Buck / Harchi","credit_id":"6807c6d7142b09cecf899d78","order":1}],"crew":[],"id":39914}},"movie_1198984_detail_vi-VN":{"at":1773676842830,"data":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/vbkW4KerpshPZnP84w9qwSfYrhu.jpg","belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":27,"name":"Phim Kinh Dị"},{"id":53,"name":"Phim Gây Cấn"}],"homepage":"","id":1198984,"imdb_id":"tt29713093","origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"We Bury the Dead","overview":"Sau một thảm họa quân sự chưa từng có, thế giới rơi vào hỗn loạn khi những người đã chết bất ngờ sống dậy. Chính quyền trấn an rằng họ chậm chạp, vô hại – và các gia đình có thể yên tâm rằng người thân của mình vẫn còn “đâu đó”. Nhưng Ava (Daisy Ridley) không tin. Khi chồng cô mất tích trong khu cách ly, cô liều mình xâm nhập vào vùng cấm, nơi tin đồn nói rằng các xác chết đang trở nên khác thường.Giữa không khí ngột ngạt, những dãy hành lang bỏ hoang và âm thanh rền rĩ của loa cảnh báo, Ava phát hiện ra sự thật kinh hoàng: những “kẻ trở lại” không còn là nạn nhân, mà là thợ săn. Càng về sau, chúng càng nhanh hơn, khát máu hơn, như thể đang tiến hóa từng phút một. Và khi quân đội cố che giấu mọi thứ, Ava phải lựa chọn giữa chạy trốn hay đối mặt với điều đang chờ trong bóng tối — thứ có thể xóa sổ toàn bộ nhân loại nếu bị thả ra ngoài.","popularity":13.6293,"poster_path":"/xZqo0yPARmyF8TACVNyaOACkYWG.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":55570,"logo_path":"/mKD4k9RHPkauvQIQsyGb6tzNAWg.png","name":"Campfire Studios","origin_country":"US"},{"id":215935,"logo_path":"/pYh0UKZbx8WGKLDZuBkq7WwvGSH.png","name":"Gramercy Park Media","origin_country":"US"},{"id":29051,"logo_path":"/A1XlmlkNkrMe4AAeFpSHCjW68BJ.png","name":"Lotterywest","origin_country":"AU"},{"id":7888,"logo_path":"/6HhOnizpDOvKjprTl47tPqvHLvZ.png","name":"ScreenWest","origin_country":"AU"},{"id":7584,"logo_path":"/eGkfvvyf4fJTvBUR1xt1669IPA3.png","name":"Screen Australia","origin_country":"AU"},{"id":101131,"logo_path":null,"name":"The Penguin Empire","origin_country":"AU"}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"AU","name":"Australia"},{"iso_3166_1":"US","name":"United States of America"}],"release_date":"2026-01-01","revenue":3745163,"runtime":95,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Kẻ Gom Xác","video":false,"vote_average":6.146,"vote_count":123}},"person_5922607_translations":{"at":1773676859607,"data":{"id":5922607,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"George Ion","primary":true}}]}},"person_1133834_translations":{"at":1773676862824,"data":{"id":1133834,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Tyler Gregory Okonma (born March 6, 1991), better known as Tyler, The Creator, is a Grammy Award-winning rapper, record producer, and music video director. He rose to prominence as the leader and co-founder of the alternative hip hop collective Odd Future and has rapped on and produced songs for nearly every Odd Future release.","name":"Tyler, The Creator","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"טיילר, דה קריאייטור","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"تايلر، ذا كرييتور","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"タイラー・ザ・クリエイター","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"ไทเลอร์เดอะครีเอเตอร์","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"تایلر، د کریتور","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"타일러 더 크리에이터","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"Tyler Gregory Okonma，说唱歌手Tyler，The Creator在7岁时就能自己做音乐。\n\n2009年12月25日，Tyler独立发布了自己的首张Solo专辑《Bastard》，专辑充斥着阴暗的能量、低沉的伴奏和Tyler那赤裸裸的反抗全社会的灵魂。专辑被Pitchfork Media评选为了2010年十佳专辑之一。\n\n2011年2月11日，Tyler发布了单曲“Yonkers”的MV，收到了在线媒体的好评，Kanye West在自己的微博上转发这个视频的时候，将它评价为“2011年最棒的MV”。这支MV的发布也让Tyler获得了XL Recordings一张专辑的合同。\n\n2020年1月，凭借《IGOR》获得第62届格莱美奖最佳说唱专辑奖。2月19日，获得第40届全英音乐奖最佳国际男歌手奖。","name":"泰勒·奥康马","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"Tyler Gregory Okonma，説唱歌手 Tyler，The Creator 在 7 歲時就能自己做音樂。\n\n2009 年 12 月 25 日，Tyler 獨立發布了自己的首張 Solo 專輯《Bastard》，專輯充斥著陰暗的能量、低沉的伴奏和 Tyler 那赤裸裸的反抗全社會的靈魂。專輯被 Pitchfork Media 評選為了 2010 年十佳專輯之一。\n\n2011 年 2 月 11 日，Tyler 發布了單曲“Yonkers”的 MV，收到了在線媒體的好評，Kanye West 在自己的微博上轉發這個視頻的時候，將它評價為“2011 年最棒的 MV”。這支 MV 的發布也讓 Tyler 獲得了 XL Recordings 一張專輯的合同。\n\n2020 年 1 月，憑借《IGOR》獲得第 62 屆格萊美獎最佳説唱專輯獎。2 月 19 日，獲得第 40 屆全英音樂獎最佳國際男歌手獎。","name":"泰勒·奧康馬","primary":false}}]}},"movie_1622032_keywords":{"at":1773676871504,"data":{"id":1622032,"keywords":[{"id":9716,"name":"stand-up comedy"}]}},"person_70701_translations":{"at":1773676872572,"data":{"id":70701,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ken Mok","primary":true}}]}},"person_104561_translations":{"at":1773676873569,"data":{"id":104561,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Craig Haydn Roberts (born 21 January 1991) is a Welsh actor and director. He is best known for lead roles as Oliver Tate in the coming-of-age comedy-drama film Submarine (2010), David Meyers in the series Red Oaks (2014–2017) and as Rio Wellard in the television series The Story of Tracy Beaker (2004–2006).\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Craig Roberts, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.","name":"Craig Roberts","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Craig Haydn Roberts (* 21. Januar 1991 in Maesycwmmer, Caerphilly) ist ein britischer Schauspieler. Bekannt wurde Roberts durch die Rolle des Oliver Tate in Submarine, einer britischen „coming-of-age“ Dramedy.\n\nRoberts begann seine Schauspielkarriere mit Rollen in den Fernsehdramas Care (2000) und Little Pudding (2003). Danach trat er in den BBC-Serien The Story of Tracy Beaker (2004–2006) und Casualty (2005–2008) auf und spielte den Vampirfanatiker Robin Branagh in Young Dracula (2006–2008). Zudem war er in den Fernsehfilmen Kiddo (2005) und Scratching (2006) zu sehen.\n\nAuf der Bühne trat Roberts im Jahr 2008, mit der durch Großbritannien reisenden Y Touring Theatre Company, auf. Dort spielte er den jungen Ryan in Full Time, ein Stück das Rassismus, Sexismus und Homophobie im Fußball thematisiert; im Januar 2009 war er Drax, der Handlanger der bösen Königin, im Märchenspiel Schneewittchen in Worthing.\n\nIm Jahr 2010 wurde Roberts durch seine Hauptrolle in der Romanverfilmung Submarine einem größeren Publikum bekannt. Die Regie führte Richard Ayoade. Seitdem war Roberts in der BBC-Three-Fernsehserie Being Human (2011, 2012) und in dem Onlineableger Becoming Human (2011) als Adam zu sehen.\n\nFür die Band The Killers spielte er im Jahr 2012 in dem Musikvideo zu Here with Me mit. Regie führte Tim Burton und seine Schauspielkollegin war Winona Ryder. Ende 2012 begann er die Arbeit an der Comedyserie The Sheepish Approach, bei der er das Drehbuch schrieb und Regie führte.\n\nIm Jahr 2013 spielte er neben Charlotte Ritchie und Rosamund Hanson in dem Film Jolene: The Indie Folk Star mit. Zudem war er als Dom in der siebten und letzten Staffel von Skins zu sehen. Außerdem spielte er in Manic Street Preachers' Video zu Show Me the Wonder mit und führte bei dem Musikvideo Avocado, Baby von Los Campesinos! selber Regie.\n\nSeit 2014 spielt er die Hauptrolle in der Amazon-Fernsehserie Red Oaks.\n\nQuelle: Wikipedia","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Крейґ Робертс","primary":false}}]}},"movie_1638004_detail_vi-VN":{"at":1773676882989,"data":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/dWeqyh9bsBsCgGbN6m8i799pyD4.jpg","belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":10402,"name":"Phim Nhạc"}],"homepage":"","id":1638004,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["KR"],"original_language":"ko","original_title":"ITZY 3rd World Tour Tunnel Vision in Seoul","overview":"","popularity":0.1481,"poster_path":"/guoza2IE4CSZsxAkbC2DLgWZNjh.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":112299,"logo_path":"/aaiQLAUubyiEkdJkXKLNTT8Kxq.png","name":"JYP Entertainment","origin_country":"KR"}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"KR","name":"South Korea"}],"release_date":"2026-02-15","revenue":0,"runtime":158,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"Korean","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"ITZY 3rd World Tour Tunnel Vision in Seoul","video":true,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0}},"person_2551480_translations":{"at":1773676888726,"data":{"id":2